{"tid":2171610,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"董義士刺殺何君堯案將正式交付高等法院進行審訊","createTime":"2020-08-24T05:22:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T15:18:47.000Z","uid":240362,"like":34,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"9271a24fc278cd903ad9bafd9763c0850ca4cc8f","tid":2171610,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T05:22:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/8550\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F8550&d=aCvg504CNSeS5FxaNurzsvrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=1bafeef9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/8550</a><br />\n<br />\n#東區裁判法院第七庭<br />\n#崔美霞裁判官<br />\n#1106屯門 #提訊日<br />\n<br />\n👤董(30)<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n(1) 企圖謀殺<br />\n被控於2019年11月6日，在屯門湖翠路啟豐花園與海翠花園之間的行人路，企圖謀殺何君堯。<br />\n<br />\n(2) 傷人19<br />\n被控於同日同地，非法及惡意傷害張英才。<br />\n（上午傷人對象仍是何君堯，下午更改了）<br />\n<br />\n❌不認罪❌<br />\n<br />\n控方確認無須初級偵訊，正式交付高等法院原訟法庭進行審訊。<br />\n<br />\n‼️被告沒有保釋申請，繼續還押。"},{"pid":"40f558e163a9457a6141d6f3fec7741d7853becf","tid":2171610,"uid":14211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T05:22:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adec449d1ac5a5ae9bc23aa258654faa56fb9e7a","tid":2171610,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40f558e163a9457a6141d6f3fec7741d7853becf","tid":2171610,"uid":14211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T05:22:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T05:22:34.000Z","msg":"<i